{"tid":2208993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美禁WeChat及TikTok  專家：下一步或對阿里出手","createTime":"2020-09-19T10:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T10:51:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"62b71202b16df1ab3121699e363f6d3553d73f28","tid":2208993,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200919/2VFNALOXYRFSNC4AL2LPOCFQG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200919%2F2VFNALOXYRFSNC4AL2LPOCFQG4%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=8a5b767c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200919%2F2VFNALOXYRFSNC4AL2LPOCFQG4%2F&h=889b83b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200919/2VFNALOXYRFSNC4AL2LPOCFQG4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美禁WeChat及TikTok <br />\n專家：下一步或對阿里出手<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國商務部昨宣佈，將直接禁止國民下載WeChat及TikTok，周日（9月20日）起生效。WeChat為騰訊（700）旗下應用程式，被視為海外版微信，TikTok則是抖音的海外版平台。美國克林信大學經濟系副教授徐家健預期，美方未來會持續以強硬姿態對付中國企業，以轉化成總統選舉的籌碼，下一步或對阿里等中資電商平台出手。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：查騰訊遊戲 封殺恐未完<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jP8wobWo4rYGYmUnqFGPY9fEJ4U=/867x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OOKICXMK5FF3ZHGKKXBUM3J6RY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjP8wobWo4rYGYmUnqFGPY9fEJ4U%3D%2F867x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOOKICXMK5FF3ZHGKKXBUM3J6RY.jpg&h=ed6e9a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部在官方網站發佈新聞稿，宣佈禁止與流動應用WeChat和TikTok進行交易，在美國的網絡流動應用程式商店方面，不。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，新聞稿公佈更多針對WeChat及Tik Tok的詳細交易禁止安排，包括不得為它們在美國提供運作或優化應用程式的網絡託管服務。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rKOuH_ejSXuOTmF6SeWs0SJzebM=/609x678/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2JCZ3EGCJREZJNVYXKLLUW52VU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrKOuH_ejSXuOTmF6SeWs0SJzebM%3D%2F609x678%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2JCZ3EGCJREZJNVYXKLLUW52VU.gif&h=c21f3290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指惡意收集資料<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部指，新禁令是特朗普8月初的行政命令延伸，指中共透過該等應用程式威脅美國的國家安全和經濟，美方將透過降低中資應用程式的功能性以保障美國用戶。美國商務部。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊正採取應變措施，路透社報道指騰訊8月19日已註冊WeCom商標，並趕在行政命令生效前將WeChat改名為WeCom，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nCNBC報道，Tik Tok發聲明，稱不同意商務部的決定，並對本月20日起禁止美國境內的應用程式新下載，及自11月12日起的使用禁止的措施，感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n徐家健分析：「（特朗普）想讓選民覺得佢有做嘢。同時唔排除大選之後，分階段繼續壓制。」在是次正式對通訊軟件及社交平台下封殺令後，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"14698f0a3cadd81ce7faca3d8902c475a0fc8de1","tid":2208993,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e837a460537497b0ce90db4517648bdabeae383b","tid":2208993,"uid":41817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resources.premierleague.com/photos/2019/11/06/d0b8759c-fecd-49ee-a53c-25e12fc128e5/dele-alli.jpg?width=930&amp;height=620\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresources.premierleague.com%2Fphotos%2F2019%2F11%2F06%2Fd0b8759c-fecd-49ee-a53c-25e12fc128e5%2Fdele-alli.jpg%3Fwidth%3D930%26height%3D620&h=6cf9c337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拳王打撚死你"},{"pid":"ea350e5a6f4f7a7c331d53e4b2c719ba77bb01d3","tid":2208993,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"就係要呢D <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恥笑完做返正經野  上去connect<br />\n<br />\n<em>美國將於20/9起禁止下載TikTok WeChat &amp; 用WeChat進行交易<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gcQQaS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gcQQaS</a></em>"},{"pid":"57a3960adfd081b01d9896a2a393410bd56f169a","tid":2208993,"uid":59461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"去台灣個副國務卿同阿里好大仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a23feb5fe5d5e66bb2a2beeca5fb8fc52824327","tid":2208993,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddeae6cd40dfbf458d04d01d54e4bad12fde15e","tid":2208993,"uid":284630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"依家全世界可能誤判左一樣野<br />\n以為侵係為左選舉先搞咁多動作<br />\n其實選舉係美國打擊中共既掩護<br />\n因為侵要選, 所以要禁呢樣<br />\n因為侵要選, 所以要賣武器俾台灣<br />\n因為侵要選, 所以今日天安門已經滿佈美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2990a60b267f13f254631b111a24b4f82e4ec29","tid":2208993,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"持有aapl個班準備跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那應該會報復性ban 番蘋果"},{"pid":"6cf1e69e107e57af18cf3e501baff24405973b21","tid":2208993,"uid":86062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bddeae6cd40dfbf458d04d01d54e4bad12fde15e","tid":2208993,"uid":284630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"依家全世界可能誤判左一樣野<br />\n以為侵係為左選舉先搞咁多動作<br />\n其實選舉係美國打擊中共既掩護<br />\n因為侵要選, 所以要禁呢樣<br />\n因為侵要選, 所以要賣武器俾台灣<br />\n因為侵要選, 所以今日天安門已經滿佈美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"典型連登傻仔<br />\n又乜乜全世界誤判，又乜乜大家忽略左一點<br />\n講到全世界都唔知，得你一個知，得你睇得最通透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd0e6b1baf1b41239b216f38893224c47d79e90","tid":2208993,"uid":128923,"like":0,"disli